parameters:
That was several years ago, the day you and I first
exchanged words...

Reisha: Take that person to the dungeon immediately!! The
crime of laying hands on royalty, it must not be forgiven!!
Yes... I was saved. Thank you.

Reisha: Let's call for a medic right away. It may seem
trivial, but it could lead to something serious.
There's no need to worry. I'll be fine.

Reisha: (Oh...? The wound that was certainly visible until
just now seems to have closed up to the point of being
invisible.)

Reisha: (It was a small scratch, but perhaps I worried too
much and misjudged it...)

I'm sorry for taking your time. You may return to your
duties now.

I... just want to be alone here until my heart settles down
a bit.

Reisha: I appreciate your concern. However, if you have any
need, no matter how minor, please do not hesitate to call
me. That's what we are here for. Now, I shall take my leave.
